{"tid":1476700,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"博爾頓：中國勿在香港製造天安門廣場記憶","createTime":"2019-08-16T01:51:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T16:33:37.000Z","uid":212626,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"baa8824ea2ef8444895dd12188c602898296f34c","tid":1476700,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T01:51:38.000Z","msg":"美國國家安全顧問博爾頓（John Bolton，法新社資料圖片）接受美國之音訪問，<span style=\"color: red;\">表示中國必須小心處理香港的抗議活動，如果中國在香港製造另一段天安門廣場記憶，那會是犯下大錯。</span><br />\n<br />\n博爾頓說，中方指美國是香港連串示威的「黑手」，並刊發駐港美國外交人員的私人資訊，這些事情需要停止。<br />\n<br />\n「中方必須小心審視每一步，因為美國人記得天安門廣場，記得那個站在坦克車陣前的男人，記得民主女神像，記得中國人民要求自由民主的呼聲，也記得1989年中國政府的鎮壓，在香港製造類似的新記憶會是一個重大錯誤。」<br />\n<br />\n他表示，六四事件後中國經濟表現好，原因包括盜用美國知識產權，並強迫美國、歐洲及日本企業轉移技術。<br />\n<br />\n「中國大陸約有60%投資是經香港流入，原因是香港有一個可以信任的司法制度，以英國模式為基礎，法院被視為客觀公正。如果香港因為中國政府一個錯誤決定而失去這個聲譽，將會對中國造成重大的經濟後果。過去幾星期，美國國會的情緒波濤起伏，只要中國政府走錯一步，國會山莊便會爆發。」 <br />\n<br />\n博爾頓認為，中國國家主席習近平正在為採取甚麼行動而憂慮，也擔心中國其他人會看見香港爭取自由的精神。「美國期望，最低限度中國會維護與英國達成的協議，履行一國但兩制的承諾，香港在主權移交後50年會維持獨一無二的制度和自由。如果違反協議，北京將會面對嚴重的信譽問題。」<br />\n<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2428159/%E3%80%90%E5%8F%8D%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B%E3%80%91%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E9%A1%A7%E5%95%8F%E5%8D%9A%E7%88%BE%E9%A0%93%EF%BC%9A%E5%8B%BF%E5%9C%A8%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E8%A3%BD%E9%80%A0%E5%A4%A9%E5%AE%89%E9%96%80%E5%BB%A3%E5%A0%B4%E8%A8%98%E6%86%B6?mtc=10012\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2428159%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E5%258F%258D%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E4%25BE%258B%25E3%2580%2591%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%2589%25E9%25A1%25A7%25E5%2595%258F%25E5%258D%259A%25E7%2588%25BE%25E9%25A0%2593%25EF%25BC%259A%25E5%258B%25BF%25E5%259C%25A8%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%25A3%25BD%25E9%2580%25A0%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E5%25AE%2589%25E9%2596%2580%25E5%25BB%25A3%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E8%25A8%2598%25E6%2586%25B6%3Fmtc%3D10012&d=veK8Cd5y3rx0%2F3TK36JPEm6H7LaHGbUBdoVXdg05ZHE%3D&h=b0cf9684\" target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2428159/%E3%80%90%E5%8F%8D%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B%E3%80%91%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E9%A1%A7%E5%95%8F%E5%8D%9A%E7%88%BE%E9%A0%93%EF%BC%9A%E5%8B%BF%E5%9C%A8%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E8%A3%BD%E9%80%A0%E5%A4%A9%E5%AE%89%E9%96%80%E5%BB%A3%E5%A0%B4%E8%A8%98%E6%86%B6?mtc=10012</a>"},{"pid":"6f3bbe1a8e446a2d7be1d019a5fac603d14e80bc","tid":1476700,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T01:53:47.000Z","msg":"美國品客<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6003fcf709dda48176f4b775f3e52edfde6dac7d","tid":1476700,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T01:54:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45c7bf82a6e0c52880145419b9c4f48494c14810","tid":1476700,"uid":99941,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T01:56:08.000Z","msg":"一早無信譽 仲點會有信譽問題"},{"pid":"d1e18572baa3e4bfb262856df80b23356d744904","tid":1476700,"uid":58345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T01:57:05.000Z","msg":"屌仲五十年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aeea531e6ce5bc1f077e1099e654d12be5788690","tid":1476700,"uid":171259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T01:58:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c44bcdfcc89739a02f5bdf83b5066a61f6bd6d46","tid":1476700,"uid":47674,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d1e18572baa3e4bfb262856df80b23356d744904","tid":1476700,"uid":58345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T01:57:05.000Z","msg":"屌仲五十年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/d